      "content": "wait i'm a bit confused. you said it \"may\" interact but then said some might be safe. i've read a lot about how grapefruit is a superfood and full of vitamins. i don't really have time to call my doctor right this second and i'm already eating. is it really that big of a deal if i just have this one glass? it's not like i'm drinking it all day.",
